I'm the idol VTuber, Hoshimachi Suisei!

396
00:45:40,629 --> 00:45:43,129
すいちゃんはー？
Sui-chan wa—?

397
00:45:43,129 --> 00:45:50,129
あー、分かる、分かる。あ、すごい分かる！すごい分かる！
Ah, I can tell, I can tell. Oh, I can totally tell! I can totally tell!

398
00:45:50,129 --> 00:45:54,129
あー、いいですね。「今日も可愛い」聞こえてきました。ありがとうございます。
Ah, that's great. I could hear "Kyou mo Kawaii". Thank you very much.

399
00:45:54,129 --> 00:45:58,629
