400
00:45:58,629 --> 00:46:03,129
“STELLAR into the GALAXY” Supported By Bushiroad へようこそ！
"STELLAR into the GALAXY" Supported By Bushiroad!

401
00:46:03,129 --> 00:46:08,629
いやー、念願のね、1stソロライブ！
Wow, the long-awaited 1st solo live!

402
00:46:08,629 --> 00:46:13,629
しかも豊洲PITということで、本当にこの日を待ち望んで、
And at Toyosu PIT, too. I've really been looking forward to this day,

403
00:46:13,629 --> 00:46:18,629
もう何ヶ月も準備をして参りましたが、
and have been preparing for months.

404
00:46:18,629 --> 00:46:23,129
