Okay, men, raise your hands!

411
00:46:58,129 --> 00:47:00,129
いっぱーい！
So many!

412
00:47:00,129 --> 00:47:03,129
はい、女性の人挙手！
Okay, women, raise your hands!

413
00:47:03,129 --> 00:47:05,129
あ、いっぱーい！
Ah, so many!

